          "data": {
            "text/plain": "Created method is_BST_. However, it cannot be invoked or used or instantiated until variable data is declared\nCreated method is_BST_. However, it cannot be referenced until variable data is declared\nAttempt to use definition snippet with unresolved references in MethodSnippet:is_BST_/(BinaryTreeNode<Integer>,Integer,Integer)boolean-public boolean is_BST_(BinaryTreeNode<Integer> node, Integer min, Integer max){\r\n    if(node == null){\r\n        return true;\r\n    }\r\n    else{\r\n        if(min != null && node.data.compareTo(min)<0 ){\r\n            return false;\r\n        }\r\n        if(max!= null && node.data.compareTo(max)>0){\r\n            return false;\r\n        }\r\n        return (is_BST_(node.left, min, node.data) && is_BST_(node.right, node.data, max));\r\n    }\r\n }\n"
